00:20:51.497 --> 00:21:06.880
It's going to take the new Reinhard Bonnkes, the new George Whitefields, the new William Seymours, and the John G.

00:21:06.880 --> 00:21:17.034
Lakes to say, 'Satan, we're taking the land back for Jesus.

00:21:17.034 --> 00:21:32.260
' We've never seen the wells of revival that are about to come on the I-35 corridor—uninterrupted glory.

00:21:34.204 --> 00:21:43.744
The Devil himself has visited my house twice, and he is a defeated foe.

00:21:43.744 --> 00:21:55.289
